sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API as API/Service Layer
    participant Facade as Business Facade
    participant BL as Business Logic Layer
    participant DB as Database Layer

    %% Étape 1 : L'utilisateur soumet le formulaire
    User->>API: Submit new place form (title, description, price, location, amenities)

    %% Étape 2 : Validation API
    API->>API: Validate request body & authentication
    API-->>User: 400 Bad Request (missing or malformed fields)
    API-->>User: 401 Unauthorized (invalid/missing token)

    %% Étape 3 : Appel à la Facade
    API->>Facade: createPlace(data, userId)

    %% Étape 4 : Validation logique + règles métier
    Facade->>BL: Validate input & ownership
    BL-->>Facade: 404 Not Found (user not found)

    %% Étape 5 : Persistance
    BL->>DB: Insert new place with owner reference
    DB-->>BL: Confirmation of place creation

    %% Étape 6 : Retour du BL
    BL-->>Facade: Return success or error

    %% Étape 7 : Retour Facade → API
    Facade-->>API: Return final result

    %% Étape 8 : Retour API → User
    API-->>User: 200 OK (place created successfully)